title: Popgun Vol 1
description:
Popgun Vol 1

Image Comics, 2007, 450 pages

PopGun is a graphic mixtape crossing the protected borders of every genre, fulfilling the desires of anyone hungry for the pungent taste of creativity. Features tracks by well-known names doing work they're not known for, brand-new talent set to change the industry and rare b-sides unearthed for the first time in years.

Far too many contributors to list. I mean, seriously, there's a lot of them. Just a few of them are Jonathon Hickman, Micheal Allred, Laura Allred, Bernie Mireault, Jim Mahfood, Rick Remember, Mark Sable, Erik Larsen and Joseph Michael Linsner.

Here's a longer list of contributors...
